    slug: "best-instagram-hashtags-for-growth-in-2026",
    title: "Best Instagram Hashtags for Growth in 2026",
    excerpt: "A realistic guide to using Instagram hashtags for reach, relevance, and niche discovery without relying on spammy lists or generic growth myths.",
    date: "March 31, 2026",
