    slug: "crush-calculator-fun-vs-real-signals",
    title: "Crush Calculator: Fun Scores vs Real Relationship Signals",
    excerpt: "Crush scores are fun, but real attraction depends on real behavior. Here is how to use the tool the right way.",
    date: "March 31, 2026",
    author: "Sneha Patel",
